examples.english: Tell me everything, from A to Z.

examples.text: Hän oli menossa, ööh… kokoukseen, luulisin.
examples.english: She was going to, erm… the meeting, I think.

glosses: uh, erm, um (expression of confusion or uncertainty)

words.etymology_text: From aakkosjärjestys by replacing the first letter of the Finnish alphabet (a) with the last (ö) and adaptation to vowel harmony.
